OL,6,FA Serious Organised Crime Unit (SOCU)
OL,7,Finvestigation began after a local
OL,8,Fpolicing officer linked a series of
OL,9,Fthefts to a single burglary last year.
OL,11,FOn 18 April 2024, a burglary took
OL,12,Fplace in Hertford which involved the
OL,13,Ftheft of car keys from inside a home.
OL,15,FThe car, a Cupra Formentor, was stolen
OL,16,Ffrom the driveway.
