OL,6,FPolice say Reid and Jones then used
OL,7,Fthis car as a getaway vehicle to
OL,8,Ffacilitate a further 38 vehicle
OL,9,Fthefts, until August, when the Cupra
OL,10,Fwas found by officers abandoned in
OL,11,FWaltham Abbey.
OL,13,FAfter the vehicle was recovered, there
OL,14,Fwas a lack of offending for around two
OL,15,Fweeks.
OL,17,FThe investigative team believed this
OL,18,Fwas because Reid and Jones were
OL,19,Fattempting to source a replacement
OL,20,Fvehicle to facilitate further thefts.
