OL,6,FBy mid-August last year, the Cupra had
OL,7,Fbeen replaced with a Volkswagen Golf,
OL,8,Fwhich was stolen from outside an
OL,9,Faddress in Edmonton.
OL,11,FReid and Jones went on to use the Golf
OL,12,Fto facilitate frequent vehicle thefts
OL,13,Facross Essex, including in Brentwood,
OL,14,FEpping, Basildon and Sudbury.
OL,16,FIn October last year, the Golf was
OL,17,Fpresent at four separate incidents,
OL,18,Fbefore Essex police officers struck.
