OL,6,FAfter a series of thefts, a search of
OL,7,Fa lockup at Waltham Abbey uncovered a
OL,8,Fstolen Ford Fiesta which was in the
OL,9,Fprocess of being stripped down for
OL,10,Fparts.
OL,12,FA variety of number plates, vehicle
OL,13,Fkeys, universal keys, balaclavas and
OL,14,Ftransmitters were uncovered.
OL,16,FFour stolen vehicles, parked outside
OL,17,Fthe garage, were also found.
