OL,6,FDCI Justin Beacher from Essex Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Painstaking hours of detective
OL,8,Fwork, going round, revisiting all the
OL,9,Fcrimes individually.
OL,11,F"Looking at CCTV, Ring doorbell, ANPR
OL,12,Fwork, and once we identified them, it
OL,13,Fwas then a case of linking them and
OL,14,Fcatching them in the act."
OL,16,FThe pair were charged with and later
OL,17,Fadmitted conspiring to commit burglary
OL,18,Fand conspiring to steal motor vehicles.
