OL,4,Cvehicles worth more than #1.3 million
OL,6,FAppearing at Chelmsford Crown Court on
OL,7,FTuesday 4 March, Reid was jailed for
OL,8,Fthree years and nine months, while
OL,9,FJones was sentenced to four years and
OL,10,F11 months imprisonment.
OL,12,FThe work of teams across Essex Police
OL,13,Fled to a fall in vehicle crime across
OL,14,Fthe past year.
OL,16,FIn the 12 months to January 2025, the
OL,17,Fauthority recorded a 5% decrease in
OL,18,Fthe number of incidents of theft of a
OL,19,Fmotor vehicle, solving 78 more cases
OL,20,Fthan they did the previous year.
